In my opinion the following changes should be made:<br>
<br>
1. Ikatair and Eashen moved to a joint rotation seperate from NTOV.<br>
2. Those guilds on NTOV should be put on the top of the Ikatair and Eashen rotation.<br>
3. The NTOV Rotation should be amended such that to receive a shot at Aaroynar you must have killed both Ikatair and Eashen, and wait for your turn on the Ikatair and Eashen Rotation before attempting Aaroynar.  This keeps the current difficulty in joining the NTOV rotation.<br>
4. In order to receive a shot at Ikatair or Eashen to join the rotation you must have demonstrated your ability to kill either Dozekor, Lendinara, Grozzrem or Telkronar.  This prevents just anyone from attempting Ikatair and Eashen.<br>
