6. The guild up for Ikatair or Eashen should have a 24 hour window from their spawn to kill them, if a guild is up for both Ikatair and Eashen rotation and NTOV, they may have till the end of their NTOV Rotation period, or 24 hours after Ikatair or Eashen spawns whichever is latest.  This will help offset the raid times for NTOV and Ikatair/Eashen, as NTOV you have 48 hours, while not making NTOV Rotation guilds make 2 trips in a single week. <p><a href="http://www.yopolis.com/syndicate" target="_blank">
