Its really not that hard to figure out, some guilds can do those 2 and not NToV.  Sooooooooo why not kill them and leave NToV for the guilds who are capable of that and when you are ready then move onto that?<br>
<br>
As far as loot goes, everyone knows that BoTS are the best equiped guild on the server and some of your members wear gear off those 2.  So why not try and farm them for what they have?<br>
<br>
All I was doing here is asking......If you are capable of killing those two mobs why are you told that you can not?  NOT on a rotation but hey if your in the neighborhood........ <p><center><BR><font color= Blue><BR><i>Granitfist/Jeribu<i/><BR><i>GrandMaster/High Priest<i/><BR><i>Co-Leader of Circles End<i/><BR><i>The Rathe<BR><center><i><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=370733">The Monk </> <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=370756">The Cleric<i/>
